classificationResult

Class ClassifiedInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • classificationResult.ClassifiedInstance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<ClassifiedInstance>

    public class ClassifiedInstance
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ClassifiedInstance>
    Object that represents an instance classified by a single classifier or by ensamble of classifiers (id, classifier confidence for each label and actual label)

      • getCombinedConfidence

        public double getCombinedConfidence()
        Get the combined confidence (confidence of the co-training style ensemble) that the instance is correctly classified (as belonging to getPrediction() class). See Confidences.getCombinedConfidence(String). If there is only one classifier, the confidence of that classifier will be returned.
        Returns:
        the co-training style ensemble confidence that the prediction for the instance is correct.

      • getCombinedConfidence

        public double getCombinedConfidence(java.lang.String labelName)

        Parameters:
